== Special Locations ==

=== Crystal Palace ===

Between worlds:
* Accessible late game
* Contains secrets about the runes
* Key to understanding the plot

=== Foma (Lost Town) ===

Hidden location:
* Requires special item
* Ancient civilization
* Unique equipment

=== Teleport Shrine ===

Quick travel:
* Activated by Wind Rune
* Links all visited towns
* Requires MP to use

